(45, 1, 1, 44, 9, 15, 15, 'called to be an apostle', 'Paul''s Apostolic Mission', 'Both passages emphasize Paul''s role as a chosen vessel. Romans highlights his separation for the gospel, while Acts specifies his mission to bear God''s name to various groups.', 'theme', 0.5309999999999999, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
