(45, 1, 5, 44, 6, 7, 7, 'obedience to the faith', 'Obedience to the Faith', 'Both passages emphasize obedience to the faith, highlighting its importance among believers. Romans 1:5 speaks of obedience to the faith among all nations, while Acts 6:7 notes that a great company of priests were obedient to the faith in Jerusalem.', 'theme', 0.377, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
