(45, 1, 5, 46, 15, 10, 10, 'grace and apostleship', 'Connection of Grace in Ministry', 'Both passages emphasize the role of grace in the apostleship and labor of Paul. Romans 1:5 speaks of receiving grace for obedience, while 1 Corinthians 15:10 highlights grace as the source of Paul''s identity and efforts.', 'theme', 0.356, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
