(45, 1, 8, 45, 6, 17, 17, 'thank my God', 'Faith and Obedience Connection', 'This connection highlights the theme of gratitude towards God for the faith and obedience of believers. Both passages express thankfulness for the transformation from sin to faith, emphasizing the importance of doctrine in shaping their lives.', 'theme', 0.34199999999999997, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
