(45, 2, 4, 23, 30, 18, 18, 'goodness of God leadeth thee to repentance', 'God''s Goodness and Mercy', 'This connection highlights the theme of God''s goodness and mercy leading to repentance and grace. Both passages emphasize God''s patience and desire to show mercy to those who wait for Him.', 'theme', 0.46099999999999997, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(45, 2, 4, 2, 34, 6, 6, 'goodness of God', 'God''s Goodness and Longsuffering', 'Both passages emphasize God''s goodness and longsuffering. Romans highlights how God''s goodness leads to repentance, while Exodus describes God as merciful and longsuffering, showcasing His character.', 'theme', 0.43299999999999994, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(45, 2, 4, 45, 9, 22, 23, 'longsuffering', 'God''s Longsuffering and Goodness', 'Both passages emphasize God''s longsuffering and goodness. Romans 2:4 highlights how God''s goodness leads to repentance, while Romans 9:22-23 discusses God''s longsuffering towards vessels of wrath to reveal His glory.', 'theme', 0.412, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(45, 2, 4, 56, 3, 4, 6, 'goodness of God leadeth thee to repentance', 'God''s Kindness and Salvation', 'This connection highlights the theme of God''s goodness and kindness leading to salvation. Both passages emphasize God''s mercy and the transformative power of His love in bringing about repentance and regeneration.', 'theme', 0.412, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(45, 2, 4, 19, 86, 15, 15, 'longsuffering', 'God''s Compassion and Longsuffering', 'Both passages emphasize God''s longsuffering and goodness, highlighting His compassionate nature. Romans 2:4 suggests that God''s goodness leads to repentance, while Psalms 86:15 describes Him as full of compassion and longsuffering.', 'theme', 0.377, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(45, 2, 4, 49, 1, 18, 18, 'riches of his goodness', 'Riches of God''s Goodness', 'This connection highlights the theme of God''s riches in both passages. Romans speaks of the ''riches of his goodness,'' while Ephesians refers to ''the riches of the glory of his inheritance,'' emphasizing the abundance of God''s grace and blessings.', 'theme', 0.377, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
