(45, 2, 9, 42, 24, 47, 47, 'doeth evil', 'Judgment and Salvation Connection', 'This connection highlights the theme of judgment for wrongdoing in Romans, which contrasts with the call for repentance and remission of sins in Luke. Both passages emphasize the need for accountability and the offer of salvation to all people.', 'theme', 0.321, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
