(45, 2, 16, 44, 17, 31, 31, 'by Jesus Christ', 'Judgment by Jesus Christ', 'Both passages emphasize God''s judgment through Jesus Christ. Romans 2:16 mentions God judging secrets by Jesus, while Acts 17:31 states He will judge the world by the ordained man, Jesus. This connection highlights the central role of Jesus in divine judgment.', 'theme', 0.356, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
