(45, 2, 17, 45, 2, 23, 23, 'makest thy boast of God', 'Boasting in the Law', 'Both passages emphasize the act of boasting in the law. Romans 2:17 states, ''makest thy boast of God,'' while Romans 2:23 questions the validity of such boasting when one breaks the law.', 'theme', 0.363, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
