(45, 3, 5, 19, 94, 1, 2, 'vengeance', 'Connection of Divine Vengeance', 'Both passages emphasize God''s role in vengeance. Romans questions God''s righteousness in taking vengeance, while Psalms directly calls upon God to render vengeance.', 'theme', 0.314, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
