(45, 3, 10, 19, 53, 1, 3, 'there is none righteous, no, not one', 'Righteousness and Human Corruption', 'Both passages emphasize the absence of righteousness among humanity. Romans 3:10 directly quotes the phrase ''there is none righteous, no, not one,'' which parallels the assertion in Psalms 53:3 that ''there is none that doeth good, no, not one.''', 'quotation', 0.6639999999999999, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
