(45, 4, 16, 48, 3, 22, 22, 'the promise might be sure to all the seed', 'Faith and Promise Connection', 'Both passages emphasize the role of faith in receiving the promise. Romans highlights the faith of Abraham, while Galatians points to the faith of Jesus Christ as the means for believers to access the promise.', 'theme', 0.32799999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
