(45, 4, 17, 43, 5, 21, 21, 'quickeneth the dead', 'Connection of Quickening the Dead', 'This connection highlights the theme of God and the Son both having the power to quicken the dead. Both passages emphasize the act of bringing life to those who are dead, showcasing a shared divine authority.', 'theme', 0.517, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
