(45, 11, 1, 24, 33, 24, 26, 'Hath God cast away his people?', 'God''s Covenant with Israel', 'Both passages emphasize God''s commitment to Israel and the continuity of His covenant. Romans 11:1 asserts that God has not cast away His people, paralleling Jeremiah 33:24-26, which discusses the enduring nature of God''s covenant with the seed of Jacob.', 'theme', 0.37, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
