(45, 14, 3, 40, 7, 1, 2, 'judge him that eateth', 'Judgment and Acceptance in Faith', 'Both passages emphasize the importance of not judging others. Romans 14:3 highlights acceptance among believers, while Matthew 7:1-2 warns against judgment, suggesting a mutual theme of grace and understanding.', 'theme', 0.32799999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
