(45, 15, 1, 45, 14, 1, 1, 'bear the infirmities of the weak', 'Strength and Weakness in Faith', 'Both passages emphasize the importance of supporting those who are weak in faith. Romans 15:1 calls the strong to bear the infirmities of the weak, while Romans 14:1 encourages receiving the weak without engaging in disputes.', 'theme', 0.601, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
