(45, 15, 1, 46, 9, 22, 22, 'bear the infirmities of the weak', 'Strength and Weakness in Community', 'Both passages emphasize the importance of supporting the weak. Romans 15:1 calls for the strong to bear the infirmities of the weak, while 1 Corinthians 9:22 illustrates the willingness to become weak for the sake of gaining others.', 'theme', 0.503, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
