(45, 15, 3, 47, 8, 9, 9, 'The reproaches of them that reproached thee fell on me', 'Connection of Christ''s Sacrifice', 'Both passages emphasize Christ''s selflessness and sacrifice for others. Romans 15:3 highlights how Christ bore reproaches, while 2 Corinthians 8:9 illustrates His choice to become poor for humanity''s benefit.', 'theme', 0.34199999999999997, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
