(45, 15, 14, 46, 8, 1, 1, 'filled with all knowledge', 'Connection of Knowledge and Charity', 'Both passages emphasize the importance of knowledge in the Christian community. Romans highlights being ''filled with all knowledge,'' while Corinthians warns that ''knowledge puffeth up,'' suggesting a need for love to build up the community.', 'theme', 0.33499999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
