(45, 15, 15, 45, 1, 5, 5, 'grace that is given to me', 'Connection of Grace in Romans', 'Both passages emphasize the concept of grace given by God. Romans 15:15 refers to the grace given to Paul, while Romans 1:5 mentions receiving grace for apostleship, linking their roles in spreading faith.', 'theme', 0.32799999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
