(45, 15, 17, 47, 2, 14, 16, 'glory through Jesus Christ', 'Triumph and Glory in Christ', 'Both passages emphasize the glory and triumph found in Christ. Romans 15:17 speaks of glory through Jesus Christ, while 2 Corinthians 2:14 highlights triumph in Christ, linking the two through their focus on Christ''s significance in believers'' lives.', 'theme', 0.356, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
